an employee has been with an organization or in a specific facility, department/unit or job) often is the determining factor for deciding matters like shifts, schedules and vacations in unionized workplaces.</td>\r\n<td width=\"72\"></td>\r\n<td width=\"72\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"31\"><strong>6</strong></td>\r\n<td width=\"449\">If my co-workers and I unionize, we wouldn’t have to work overtime again.</td>\r\n<td width=\"72\"></td>\r\n<td width=\"72\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"31\"><strong>7</strong></td>\r\n<td width=\"449\">My manager and I would still be able to work together to create a schedule that meets my individual needs because of my childcare, adult care or education demands.</td>\r\n<td width=\"72\"></td>\r\n<td width=\"72\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"31\"><strong>8</strong></td>\r\n<td width=\"449\">Labor unions have the right to spend members’ dues any way they want without asking members what they think.</td>\r\n<td width=\"72\"></td>\r\n<td width=\"72\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"31\"><strong>9</strong></td>\r\n<td width=\"449\">Unions are legally allowed to make promises during campaigns that they are not willing or able to keep.</td>\r\n<td width=\"72\"></td>\r\n<td width=\"72\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width=\"31\"><strong>10</strong></td>\r\n<td width=\"449\">The union needs to collect signatures from only 30% of the targeted employee group in order to get a secret ballot election.</td>\r\n<td width=\"72\"></td>\r\n<td width=\"72\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\nAnswers: 1. False; 2. False; 3. False; 4. True; 5. True; 6. False; 7. False; 8. True; 9. True; 10. True','How Well Do You Know the Facts About Unions?','','publish','closed','closed','','how-well-do-you-know-the-facts-about-unions','','','2017-01-17 19:09:30','2017-01-18 00:09:30','',0,'https://baycareknowthefacts.org/?p=147',0,'post','',0),(148,2,'2017-01-12 19:55:22','2017-01-13 00:55:22','','how-well-do